### Warlord Traits

* One HQ character model in a player’s army must be designated as the army’s **WARLORD**.  
* A **WARLORD** receives one trait from the **WARLORD TRAIT** table below of the player’s choice. If the army’s codex provides its own set of warlord traits (or the equivalent types of the effects), those may be used instead of selecting  a trait from the table below (and players may directly select which trait to use in either case).

| Inspiring Presence Friendly units within 12" of the Warlord can use his Leadership rather than their own. | The Dust of a Thousand Worlds Your Warlord, and all friendly units within 12", have the Move Through Cover special rule. | Master of Maneuver Your Warlord has the Outflank special rule (not conferred to units he joins). |
| :---- | :---- | :---- |
| **Target Priority** In the Shooting phase, your Warlord and all friendly units within 12" of him reroll To Hit rolls of 1\. | **Master of Defense** Your Warlord has the Counter-attack special rule. | **Tenacity** Your Warlord has the Feel No Pain special rule (5+). |
| **Coordinated Assault** In the Assault phase, your Warlord and all friendly units within 12" of him reroll To Hit rolls of 1\. | **Master of Offense** Your Warlord has the Furious Charge special rule. | **Strategic Genius** Whilst your Warlord is alive, you can re-roll any Reserve Rolls. |
